/**
 * OverlayController.tsx
 *
 * Single mount point for every overlay in the app — dialogs, sheets, modals,
 * windows, toasts. Renders the appropriate component when slice state says so,
 * with every prop wired by name (no `{...spread}`) so TypeScript catches
 * dispatch / component prop-shape drift at compile time.
 *
 * Initial seed generated by `scripts/generate-overlay-controller.ts` from the
 * old window-panels registry. Subsequent edits are hand-written.
 *
 * Rules (ESLint-enforced):
 *   - No JSX prop spread in this file.
 *   - Every overlayId in OVERLAY_IDS is rendered here exactly once.
 */
